repositories.name: slnq-ai-app
repositories.title: SLNQ: Youth Support Services Management Platform
repositories.description: A sophisticated, AI-enhanced youth support services management platform for residential care operations for vulnerable young people in Queensland, Australia. Features voice-to-text transcription, intelligent document generation, pattern recognition for risk assessment, and automated compliance monitoring.
repositories.abstract: Safe Living NQ represents a comprehensive AI-enhanced platform revolutionising residential care operations for vulnerable young people. Built on Nuxt 3's server-side architecture and powered by Supabase's real-time infrastructure, it delivers comprehensive case management, staff coordination, facility oversight, and compliance monitoring specifically designed for youth residential care environments.

repositories.name: warringu-app
repositories.title: Warringu: Specialised Shared Services Hub
repositories.description: A Flutter web application providing integrated access to specialist services for indigenous organizations. Features secure user authentication, case management systems, and training modules.
repositories.abstract: A Flutter web application providing integrated access to specialist services for the Warringu organization. Features responsive two-column layout with embedded Koori Grapevine website, secure authentication for three user types, and integration with case management, HR, and training systems including Circles of Security and Safe and Together.

repositories.name: FNQPHNRiskStratificationTool
repositories.title: FNQ PHN Risk Stratification Tool
repositories.description: An advanced healthcare risk stratification platform using machine learning for primary care analytics. Features AI-powered analysis, geospatial integration, and ensemble learning algorithms.
repositories.abstract: An enterprise-grade healthcare risk stratification platform designed for Far North Queensland Primary Health Network. Utilizes ensemble machine learning algorithms to analyze patient data, identify high-risk individuals, and provide actionable insights for preventive care interventions. Integrates geospatial analysis for population health management.
highlights: Ensemble ML algorithms for risk prediction

repositories.name: OrthoVision
repositories.title: OrthoVision: AI-Powered Orthopaedic Diagnostics
repositories.description: A comprehensive AI platform for orthopaedic diagnostics featuring HorusAI (clinical consultation), HarrierX (computer vision diagnostics), and LammerGAN (synthetic medical image generation).
repositories.abstract: OrthoVision is a comprehensive AI platform for orthopaedic diagnostics combining three core modules: HorusAI for intelligent clinical consultation, HarrierX for computer vision-based diagnostic analysis using YOLOv8, and LammerGAN for generating synthetic medical images. Built with TensorFlow and PyTorch for state-of-the-art deep learning capabilities.

repositories.name: help-now
repositories.title: HelpNow: Comprehensive Emergency Response and Community Support Platform
repositories.description: An innovative, AI-enhanced emergency response and community support platform engineered to revolutionise crisis management, resource coordination, and community assistance delivery. Built with React, Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and Flutter for comprehensive emergency response coordination.
repositories.abstract: HelpNow represents an innovative, AI-enhanced emergency response and community support platform engineered to revolutionise crisis management, resource coordination, and community assistance delivery. Built upon modern full-stack architecture combining React frontend, Node.js/Express backend, and MongoDB data persistence, the platform delivers comprehensive emergency response coordination designed for emergency services, community organisations, and crisis response teams.
highlights: Rapid crisis response with intelligent automation

repositories.name: evolutionary-biology-analysis
repositories.title: Evolutionary Biology Analysis Suite
repositories.description: Comprehensive R-based toolkit for evolutionary biology research including genetic drift simulation, phylogenetic analysis, population genetics modeling, and molecular evolution studies.
repositories.abstract: Advanced computational toolkit for evolutionary biology research providing simulation capabilities, statistical analysis, and visualization tools for genetic studies, population dynamics, and phylogenetic reconstruction.

repositories.name: mwd-weekly-dashboard
repositories.title: My Weekly Dash: Comprehensive Goal Achievement and Productivity Platform
repositories.description: A comprehensive goal achievement and productivity platform engineered to transform personal and professional development through structured goal-setting methodologies, accountability systems, and intelligent progress tracking.
repositories.abstract: My Weekly Dash represents a comprehensive goal achievement and productivity platform built on Flutter and Supabase, implementing evidence-based productivity principles including SMART goal frameworks, spaced repetition techniques, and social accountability mechanisms. Through integrated daily check-ins, weekly planning sessions, and collaborative sharing features, it bridges the gap between aspiration and achievement.
highlights: SMART goal framework integration with progress tracking
Cross-platform Flutter applications (iOS, Android, Web, Desktop)
Advanced analytics dashboard with trend analysis

repositories.name: kait-conversational-ai
repositories.title: KAITY: Advanced Customer Service & Business Intelligence Platform
repositories.description: A comprehensive customer service and business intelligence platform built with Vue.js 3 and Supabase, featuring automated customer communication management, intelligent business analysis, FAQ generation, and real-time analytics for operational optimisation.
repositories.abstract: KAITY provides comprehensive customer service and business intelligence capabilities through automated communication management, intelligent business analysis, and real-time operational insights. Features sophisticated FAQ generation, customer interaction tracking, and data-driven business optimisation frameworks.

repositories.name: plaict-community-dashboard
repositories.title: PLAICT: Community Engagement Analytics Platform
repositories.description: A comprehensive community engagement analytics platform featuring data visualization, user interaction tracking, and community health metrics. Built for supporting community organizations and engagement initiatives.
repositories.abstract: PLAICT provides comprehensive analytics for community engagement initiatives, featuring advanced data visualization, user interaction tracking, and community health metrics to support organizational decision-making and community development.

repositories.name: kidmaps-dashboard
repositories.title: KidMaps Dashboard: Business Event & Location Management
repositories.description: A comprehensive business management platform enabling local businesses to manage their events, locations, and customer engagement. Features event scheduling, location management, customer communications, and analytics dashboard for business optimization.
repositories.abstract: KidMaps Dashboard provides businesses with comprehensive tools for managing events and locations. Built with Vue.js 3 and Supabase, it features event scheduling systems, location management tools, customer engagement features, and analytics dashboards specifically designed for local businesses to optimize their operations and community presence.

repositories.name: kidmaps-app
repositories.title: KidMaps: Geospatial Mobile Application for Family Services
repositories.description: A sophisticated cross-platform mobile application that addresses the fragmentation of family activity information systems. KidMaps provides unified mobile experience for families seeking activities and organizations managing events.
repositories.abstract: KidMaps represents a novel approach to family-centric geospatial information systems (GIS), providing comprehensive location-based services for families. Built with Flutter for cross-platform compatibility, it features advanced geospatial algorithms, real-time data synchronization, and comprehensive security with JWT authentication.
highlights: Interactive geospatial mapping with real-time location tracking
Event discovery and booking with Stripe payment integration
Push notifications via Firebase Cloud Messaging
QR code generation for ticket validation

repositories.name: WAIVI
repositories.title: WAIVI: Weighted Adaptive Intelligence for Vegetable and Fruit Identification
repositories.description: A comprehensive computer vision framework for real-time produce classification and detection using state-of-the-art YOLO architectures. Optimized for multi-class fruit and vegetable recognition across 32 distinct categories.
repositories.abstract: WAIVI presents a comprehensive computer vision framework for real-time produce classification and detection, employing YOLOv8 architectures optimized for multi-class fruit and vegetable recognition. The system demonstrates superior performance in challenging conditions including variable lighting, occlusion, and scale variations commonly encountered in agricultural and retail environments.
highlights: YOLOv8 architecture optimization for agricultural applications
Edge computing deployment with ONNX and HEF formats
Multi-scale training and curriculum learning strategies
Mobile integration for iOS and Android platforms

repositories.name: play_leaf_green
repositories.title: Pokemon AI Agent: Memory-Driven Autonomous Game Playing
repositories.description: A hybrid Rust-Python system for autonomous Pokemon gameplay using memory-driven intelligence. Features DeepSeek LLM integration, persistent experience database tracking 250 recent memories, OCR text extraction, pathfinding with fallback strategies, and adaptive learning from action outcomes.
repositories.abstract: The Pokemon AI Agent represents an advanced autonomous game-playing system combining Rust's performance for emulator interaction with Python's AI capabilities. It implements memory-driven intelligence where game state is tracked as a contextual diary, enabling adaptive learning from past experiences. The system achieves sub-100ms response times while maintaining sophisticated understanding through OCR, pathfinding, and success/failure tracking.
highlights: Rust for high-performance memory reading and emulator control
Python AI orchestration with DeepSeek integration
OCR-based text extraction for dialogue understanding
A* pathfinding with adjacent movement fallback
92% navigation success rate with fallback strategies
